# Code owners for high-risk / high-scrutiny paths.
# See docs/scaling-tech-challenges.md, Security Vulnerabilities #10:
# AGENTS.md / CLAUDE.md instruct AI coding agents to read/execute guidance
# from arbitrary repo paths. A compromised dependency or a malicious PR could
# plant similar "agent instructions" that get silently obeyed by AI coding
# assistants. Changes to these files require a second, human reviewer — do
# not let an AI agent approve or auto-merge changes to them.
#
# NOTE: replace @wanderplanner/maintainers below with a real GitHub team/user
# handle for this repo, then enable "Require review from Code Owners" in
# branch protection settings for this to actually gate merges.

/apps/web/AGENTS.md      @wanderplanner/maintainers
/apps/web/CLAUDE.md      @wanderplanner/maintainers
**/AGENTS.md             @wanderplanner/maintainers
**/CLAUDE.md             @wanderplanner/maintainers
